+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
                         INNER STRENGTH
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

	Level: 15
	Cost: 50
	Text: summon inner strength

	By the use of his mind a psionicist can summon forth a great
	amount of inner strength. While in this state the psionicist
	will be stronger and able to take more hits. The only draw back
	to this power is that when the psionicist leaves this state of
	mind after a short time, he will be in worest shape then when
	he entered the state of inner strength. This is a very strong
	power so watch yourself when you use it!

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
